These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: fanta, cola, juice, milk
Pet: cat, frog, turtle, pony
1. Pet:pony is on the left of Beverage:juice##1
2. Beverage:fanta is on the left of Pet:frog##1
3. Beverage:milk is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:turtle is on the left or right of Pet:pony##3
5. Beverage:fanta is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | cola | milk | juice |
| Pet        | cat | frog   | pony | turtle    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: horror, spy, family, sports
Nationality: indonesian, american, chinese, thai
1. Movie-Genre:spy is on the left of Movie-Genre:sports##1
2. Nationality:indonesian is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1
3. Nationality:chinese is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:indonesian == Movie-Genre:horror##1
5. Nationality:american is on the right of Nationality:chinese##1
6. Nationality:indonesian == Movie-Genre:horror##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | horror  | spy  | sports |
| Nationality   | thai    | indonesian | chinese | american    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: mango, peach, cranberry, onion
Movie-Genre: sports, comedy, adventure, fantasy
1. Food:onion is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:fantasy##3
2. Food:cranberry is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:fantasy is on the left or right of Food:peach##3
4. Movie-Genre:fantasy is on the right of Movie-Genre:adventure##1
5. Movie-Genre:sports is in an odd position##4
6. Food:peach is on the right of Food:cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | onion | cranberry | peach    | mango      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure        | fantasy     | sports | comedy |

