.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: puzzles, card-games, writing, traveling
Music-Genre: rock, trance, house, metal
1. Hobby:card-games is between Music-Genre:rock and Music-Genre:metal##2
2. Hobby:traveling is on the left of Hobby:puzzles##1
3. Music-Genre:house is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:trance is on the left of Music-Genre:metal##1
5. Music-Genre:trance is on the right of Hobby:puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling | puzzles | card-games | writing |
| Music-Genre   | house       | rock   | trance    | metal  |

