2. Beverage:coffee is on the left or right of Beverage:juice##3
3. Beverage:almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:apricot is on the left of Food:lemon##1
5. Food:lemon is on the right of Beverage:juice##1
6. Food:apricot is in an even position##4
7. Food:garlic == Beverage:tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | juice    | coffee       | tea |
| Food       | onion  | apricot | lemon | garlic  |

